  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 10 OF CHAPTER 534, LAWS OF 2024, AS AMENDED BY SECTION 3 OF CHAPTER 510, LAWS OF 2025, TO ADD A NEW PROJECT TO BE FUNDED WITH MONIES DISBURSED FROM THE 2024 LOCAL IMPROVEMENTS PROJECTS FUND; TO DIRECT THE STATE TREASURER TO TRANSFER THE SUM OF $7,074,214.00 FROM THE CAPITAL EXPENSE FUND INTO THE 2024 LOCAL IMPROVEMENTS PROJECTS FUND FOR THE PURPOSE OF FUNDING THAT PROJECT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
